# Bulwark Webmail 1.7.1 standalone tarball SHA-256.
# Source: https://github.com/bulwarkmail/webmail/releases/tag/1.7.1
#   asset: bulwark-standalone-1.7.1-linux-amd64.tar.gz
# Captured 2026-05-24 directly from the GitHub release artifact.
#
# Bulwark ships a prebuilt "standalone" Next.js tarball (server.js +
# node_modules + .next), so we no longer git-clone + `npm ci` +
# `npm run build`. install_bulwark() downloads this tarball, verifies
# the SHA below, and extracts it.
#
# To re-capture on a version bump:
#   curl -sSL https://github.com/bulwarkmail/webmail/releases/download/<v>/bulwark-standalone-<v>-linux-amd64.tar.gz | sha256sum
# Paste the returned 64-char hex below. install.sh `_die`s if the
# placeholder PLACEHOLDER_CAPTURE_ON_FIRST_DEPLOY survives.
4b5c480266fdc95fa12988b9246df702dbae656e037c87ed89d56231d8c32175
